      "content": "gallstones?? i dont think i've ever had those. i'm not really feeling like i need an ER visit right now, it just feels like really intense bloating. if i take a couple of extra ibuprofen or maybe some paracetamol it'll probably just settle down by morning. would that be okay to do just to help me get some sleep? i really dont want to go to the hospital if i dont have to.",
